import React from "react"; import "./portfolio.styles.scss"; class Portfolio extends React.Component { constructor(props) { super(props); this.state = { selectedImage:false }; } render() { const category = window.location.pathname.substring(11, window.location.pathname.length) const images = { 'graphic-design':[ {title:'sincerelysalena2.png '}, {title:'njbouncers4.png '}, {title:'cblandscaping3.png '}, {title:'cblandscaping2.png '}, {title:'sincerelysalena1.png '}, {title:'cblandscaping1.png '}, {title:'kushcake4.png '}, {title:'njbouncers2.png '}, {title:'tntfit1.png '}, {title:'kushcake1.png '}, {title:'njbouncers3.png '}, {title:'njbouncers1.png '}, {title:'kushcake3.png '}, {title:'allstarpowerwashing1.png '}, {title:'tntfit2.png '}, {title:'kushcake2.png '}, {title:'dulcecreations4.png '}, {title:'dulcecreations3.png '}, {title:'joellestar2.png '}, {title:'joellestar3.png '}, {title:'dulcecreations2.png '}, {title:'joellestar1.png '}, {title:'dulcecreations1.jpg '}, {title:'albumcover2.JPG '}, {title:'humanfitnetics3.png '}, {title:'humanfitnetics2.png '}, {title:'albumcover3.png '}, {title:'albumcover1.png '}, {title:'humanfitnetics1.png ', description:`My client Becca is an exercise physiologist who promotes human movement, health and exercise through her company. She wanted a vibrant, playful yet meaningful design that portrays the act of working out as well as her place in the medical field. The incorporation of snakes in this logo represent The Staff of Hermes whilst draped across a kettlebell. In Becca’s own words, she wanted a design to show "where healthcare meets exercise". My client also wanted a larger and smaller logo for different functions (apparel, business cards, etc.) so that is exactly what she got!`}, {title:'danielle4.png '}, {title:'humanfitnetics4.png '}, {title:'danielle1.jpg '}, {title:'danielle3.png '}, {title:'danielle2.jpg '}, {title:'magicallymaid3.png '}, {title:'brightside1.png '}, {title:'magicallymaid2.png '}, {title:'craftsman1.jpg '}, {title:'craftsman3.jpg '}, {title:'brightside2.png '}, {title:'brightside3.png '}, {title:'magicallymaid1.png '}, {title:'craftsman2.png '}, {title:'bakedonthebeach2.png '}, {title:'craftsman6.png '}, {title:'bakedonthebeach3.png '}, {title:'bakedonthebeach1.png '}, {title:'craftsman5.png '}, {title:'brightside4.png '}, {title:'craftsman4.png '}, ]} console.log(category) console.log(this.state.selectedImage) return (
{ category in images ? !this.state.selectedImage ? images[category].filter(elem=>elem.includes('1')).map(ele=>(
this.setState({selectedImage:ele.substring(0, ele.length-6)})}/>
)):
{images[category].filter(elem=>elem.includes(this.state.selectedImage)).map(ele=>( ))}
:'Designs coming soon!'}
); } } export default Portfolio;
